1
00:01:31,880 --> 00:01:32,759
Mr. Ye?

2
00:01:34,680 --> 00:01:35,520
What brings you here?

3
00:01:36,240 --> 00:01:36,920
Was it you

4
00:01:37,400 --> 00:01:38,520
or Fu Hailian?

5
00:01:39,039 --> 00:01:40,680
I have no idea what you're saying.

6
00:01:42,800 --> 00:01:44,240
I think it's Fu Hailian.

7
00:01:44,560 --> 00:01:46,240
He hates the military nobles so much.

8
00:01:46,759 --> 00:01:47,800
He'd love to blow

9
00:01:48,039 --> 00:01:49,039
Great Yan's military nobles

10
00:01:49,039 --> 00:01:49,800
to bits.

11
00:01:51,479 --> 00:01:53,800
Sure, he's thought about it.

12
00:01:54,280 --> 00:01:55,640
But that's all it is.

13
00:01:57,479 --> 00:01:59,080
So I think

14
00:01:59,600 --> 00:02:00,400
it's you.

15
00:02:01,280 --> 00:02:02,520
After all, I've crossed you

16
00:02:02,520 --> 00:02:03,880
more than once.

17
00:02:04,520 --> 00:02:05,320
And you get back at people

18
00:02:05,320 --> 00:02:06,680
over the smallest slight.

19
00:02:07,280 --> 00:02:08,160
You mean

20
00:02:08,440 --> 00:02:09,280
His Majesty removing you

21
00:02:09,560 --> 00:02:10,720
as the Crown Prince's study companion?

22
00:02:12,040 --> 00:02:13,280
So it really was you.

23
00:02:13,880 --> 00:02:14,360
Yes.

24
00:02:14,800 --> 00:02:16,120
It was my duty.

25
00:02:16,400 --> 00:02:17,040
I just made

26
00:02:17,040 --> 00:02:18,360
a suggestion to His Majesty.

27
00:02:19,240 --> 00:02:20,480
It wasn't revenge.

28
00:02:20,840 --> 00:02:22,200
How dare you still deny it?

29
00:02:22,800 --> 00:02:23,720
You call me

30
00:02:23,720 --> 00:02:25,480
someone who holds a grudge.

31
00:02:25,800 --> 00:02:27,960
Taking away a Crown Prince's study companion

32
00:02:28,200 --> 00:02:29,280
is nothing.

33
00:02:31,920 --> 00:02:33,200
Then why did you do it?

34
00:02:38,600 --> 00:02:39,760
Because His Highness

35
00:02:40,120 --> 00:02:41,680
may have loyal men

36
00:02:41,960 --> 00:02:43,440
or sycophants,

37
00:02:44,280 --> 00:02:45,840
but never

38
00:02:46,560 --> 00:02:48,200
someone like you.

39
00:02:49,400 --> 00:02:50,480
What kind of person am I?

40
00:02:50,960 --> 00:02:52,160
A

41
00:02:53,520 --> 00:02:54,880
desperate one.

42
00:03:13,840 --> 00:03:14,440
Sir.

43
00:03:17,240 --> 00:03:19,120
A desperate one, huh.

44
00:03:24,480 --> 00:03:25,240
Do you know

45
00:03:26,440 --> 00:03:28,160
why Chen Yanyun said that?

46
00:03:28,440 --> 00:03:29,440
I don't.

47
00:03:30,040 --> 00:03:30,960
But I know

48
00:03:31,000 --> 00:03:32,079
he's up to no good.

49
00:03:34,000 --> 00:03:34,960
Because he's scared.

50
00:03:36,000 --> 00:03:36,920
He's scared

51
00:03:37,520 --> 00:03:38,560
I'll win the Crown Prince over.

52
00:03:41,600 --> 00:03:42,840
That actually reminds me.

53
00:03:43,400 --> 00:03:44,160
I may not be

54
00:03:44,160 --> 00:03:45,120
the Crown Prince's study companion.

55
00:03:45,800 --> 00:03:46,720
But I'm not letting

56
00:03:46,720 --> 00:03:48,160
the time I spent on him

57
00:03:49,360 --> 00:03:50,640
go to waste.

58
00:03:56,560 --> 00:03:57,000
Sir,

59
00:03:57,280 --> 00:03:58,320
if I may.

60
00:03:59,440 --> 00:04:00,800
His Majesty just ordered a probe

61
00:04:00,800 --> 00:04:01,920
into the attack on the Crown Prince,

62
00:04:02,360 --> 00:04:03,880
and you removed Mr. Ye from his post.

63
00:04:04,120 --> 00:04:04,560
Isn't that

64
00:04:05,520 --> 00:04:06,600
a bit obvious?

65
00:04:07,360 --> 00:04:08,440
Doesn't matter.

66
00:04:08,960 --> 00:04:10,360
Since the late Prince Chengqing's rebellion,

67
00:04:10,680 --> 00:04:12,160
His Majesty has been wary of military nobles.

68
00:04:12,600 --> 00:04:14,200
Now the attack on the Crown Prince

69
00:04:14,480 --> 00:04:15,440
has dragged in the late Prince Chengqing

70
00:04:15,440 --> 00:04:16,800
and Prince Glorian.

71
00:04:17,279 --> 00:04:17,880
I expect

72
00:04:18,200 --> 00:04:18,880
His Majesty will start

73
00:04:18,880 --> 00:04:20,640
cracking down on military nobles soon.

74
00:04:21,399 --> 00:04:22,640
So removing Ye Xian from his post

75
00:04:23,120 --> 00:04:24,120
is nothing but good

76
00:04:24,120 --> 00:04:24,960
for him.

77
00:04:25,480 --> 00:04:26,200
You're trying to

78
00:04:26,840 --> 00:04:27,920
protect Lord Changxing?

79
00:04:30,000 --> 00:04:30,840
Civil officials

80
00:04:31,520 --> 00:04:33,480
and military nobles may be at odds,

81
00:04:34,000 --> 00:04:35,080
but the country

82
00:04:36,920 --> 00:04:38,520
always needs its warriors.

83
00:04:39,480 --> 00:04:41,000
Lord Changxing made real contributions

84
00:04:41,080 --> 00:04:42,280
and can actually fight.

85
00:04:44,040 --> 00:04:45,480
I'll protect him whenever I can.

86
00:04:47,120 --> 00:04:47,560
Understood.

87
00:04:52,320 --> 00:04:54,640
Mr. Ye's always thinking of you.

88
00:04:54,880 --> 00:04:56,800
He knew you were bored in the palace,

89
00:04:57,000 --> 00:04:58,480
so he went out of his way to find

90
00:04:58,480 --> 00:04:59,760
all these fun little things for you.

91
00:05:01,480 --> 00:05:02,600
Too bad he can't

92
00:05:02,600 --> 00:05:03,800
come play with me in the palace anymore.

93
00:05:04,040 --> 00:05:05,240
He has a heart condition.

94
00:05:05,760 --> 00:05:06,440
I can't

95
00:05:06,440 --> 00:05:07,680
force him to stay.

96
00:05:08,040 --> 00:05:09,880
There'll be other chances.

97
00:05:25,120 --> 00:05:26,240
Hold onto this for me.

98
00:05:26,440 --> 00:05:28,240
Show it to me secretly tonight.

99
00:05:28,320 --> 00:05:28,840
Yes.

100
00:05:30,400 --> 00:05:31,840
Ye Xian really gets me.

101
00:05:32,680 --> 00:05:34,560
All my other study companions

102
00:05:34,680 --> 00:05:35,880
treat me like their master now.

103
00:05:36,040 --> 00:05:36,840
So boring.

104
00:05:37,520 --> 00:05:38,960
Ye Xian is the only one

105
00:05:42,280 --> 00:05:43,280
who treats me like a friend!

106
00:05:53,640 --> 00:05:54,880
Ye Xian does so much for me.

107
00:05:55,800 --> 00:05:58,240
I feel bad taking his gifts for nothing.

108
00:05:58,880 --> 00:06:01,280
I should give him something in return.

109
00:06:05,320 --> 00:06:06,120
Mr. Ye,

110
00:06:06,720 --> 00:06:07,960
His Highness specially

111
00:06:08,000 --> 00:06:09,640
grants you this token.

112
00:06:11,040 --> 00:06:11,720
With it,

113
00:06:11,880 --> 00:06:14,120
you may enter and leave the East Palace

114
00:06:14,280 --> 00:06:16,040
anytime without permission.

115
00:06:24,080 --> 00:06:25,280
I'm deeply moved

116
00:06:25,560 --> 00:06:26,440
by His Highness's kindness.

117
00:06:26,920 --> 00:06:28,240
I only hope to recover soon

118
00:06:28,560 --> 00:06:29,920
and continue to serve him.

119
00:06:40,800 --> 00:06:41,680
Uncle.

120
00:06:43,040 --> 00:06:43,800
What brings you here?

121
00:06:44,040 --> 00:06:44,960
What do you need?

122
00:06:45,800 --> 00:06:47,240
A classmate just sent word.

123
00:06:47,640 --> 00:06:48,400
The court has appointed

124
00:06:49,000 --> 00:06:50,159
Mr. Chang Tinglan as chief examiner

125
00:06:50,360 --> 00:06:51,640
for this year's metropolitan exam.

126
00:06:52,440 --> 00:06:53,840
You foresaw this

127
00:06:54,080 --> 00:06:55,640
and told me to seek Mr. Chang's guidance?

128
00:06:56,320 --> 00:06:57,440
Guidance is one thing.

129
00:06:57,800 --> 00:06:58,800
How much you actually learn

130
00:06:59,120 --> 00:07:00,800
depends on your own ability.

131
00:07:02,600 --> 00:07:03,560
Thank you, Uncle.

132
00:07:05,440 --> 00:07:06,040
Go on.

133
00:07:13,120 --> 00:07:13,800
I

134
00:07:14,560 --> 00:07:16,120
have one more thing to ask.

135
00:07:17,720 --> 00:07:18,880
Could you

136
00:07:19,200 --> 00:07:19,600
not

137
00:07:19,600 --> 00:07:20,920
arrange a match for me just yet?

138
00:07:21,560 --> 00:07:23,000
Wait until after the metropolitan exam.

139
00:07:23,360 --> 00:07:23,880
Why?

140
00:07:24,240 --> 00:07:25,280
You have

141
00:07:25,920 --> 00:07:27,160
someone else in mind?

142
00:07:34,520 --> 00:07:35,120
No.

143
00:07:35,720 --> 00:07:36,360
It's just...

144
00:07:37,080 --> 00:07:38,440
I don't want to rush things.

145
00:07:44,120 --> 00:07:45,680
You don't need to go to the academy today.

146
00:07:46,840 --> 00:07:48,000
Come with me somewhere.

147
00:07:50,800 --> 00:07:51,360
Yes.

148
00:08:15,840 --> 00:08:16,480
I know

149
00:08:17,320 --> 00:08:18,920
I shouldn't go against my uncle.

150
00:08:20,480 --> 00:08:21,880
He must have thought long and hard

151
00:08:22,600 --> 00:08:24,360
before arranging a match with the Yu family.

152
00:08:24,840 --> 00:08:25,360
Xuanqing.

153
00:08:26,040 --> 00:08:26,880
But I've followed

154
00:08:26,880 --> 00:08:28,280
his lead my whole life.

155
00:08:29,960 --> 00:08:31,200
This once, even if I'm wrong,

156
00:08:33,760 --> 00:08:35,120
even if it costs me,

157
00:08:35,760 --> 00:08:37,080
I have to take the chance.

158
00:08:38,640 --> 00:08:39,240
Or

159
00:08:40,720 --> 00:08:42,240
I'll regret it for the rest of my life.

160
00:08:42,679 --> 00:08:43,440
Exactly.

161
00:08:43,640 --> 00:08:44,560
I support you.

162
00:08:45,520 --> 00:08:47,640
This is a lifetime decision.

163
00:09:15,040 --> 00:09:15,480
This...

164
00:09:16,160 --> 00:09:16,880
This is the cenotaph

165
00:09:17,480 --> 00:09:19,640
of your birth father, Lin Zhengwei.

166
00:09:21,440 --> 00:09:22,520
Are you wondering

167
00:09:22,760 --> 00:09:24,080
why it's a cenotaph?

168
00:09:24,840 --> 00:09:25,680
Because

169
00:09:26,120 --> 00:09:27,280
your father committed

170
00:09:27,280 --> 00:09:28,600
an unpardonable crime.

171
00:09:29,120 --> 00:09:30,800
He was sentenced to immediate execution.

172
00:09:31,720 --> 00:09:32,440
Back then,

173
00:09:32,920 --> 00:09:33,960
I was too low in rank

174
00:09:34,440 --> 00:09:35,760
to retrieve his body.

175
00:09:38,320 --> 00:09:38,720
But...

176
00:09:39,480 --> 00:09:39,840
But...

177
00:09:41,360 --> 00:09:42,880
But didn't you tell me my father...

178
00:09:43,600 --> 00:09:44,240
my birth father

179
00:09:44,960 --> 00:09:46,560
died protecting you

180
00:09:46,960 --> 00:09:48,480
from river pirates?

181
00:09:50,240 --> 00:09:51,240
That was a lie.

182
00:09:52,000 --> 00:09:52,960
The truth is,

183
00:09:53,360 --> 00:09:54,760
Lin Zhengwei

184
00:09:55,080 --> 00:09:56,080
colluded with the river pirates

185
00:09:56,440 --> 00:09:58,080
and tipped them off about the ship's route.

186
00:09:58,400 --> 00:09:59,720
The ship went down, and people died.

187
00:10:00,080 --> 00:10:01,920
Over a hundred soldiers and officers

188
00:10:01,920 --> 00:10:03,040
drowned.

189
00:10:08,880 --> 00:10:10,920
Now, only two people

190
00:10:12,080 --> 00:10:12,920
know about this.

191
00:10:13,920 --> 00:10:14,600
One is me.

192
00:10:15,240 --> 00:10:16,040
The other is Yu Kaiji,

193
00:10:16,320 --> 00:10:17,960
the former chief of the Jiaodong section

194
00:10:18,040 --> 00:10:20,000
of the canal transport office.

195
00:10:20,560 --> 00:10:22,120
Your future father-in-law.

196
00:10:25,440 --> 00:10:26,040
Then

197
00:10:27,200 --> 00:10:28,480
why did you still take me in?

198
00:10:29,720 --> 00:10:30,720
Because your birth father

199
00:10:30,760 --> 00:10:32,160
did save my life.

200
00:10:32,600 --> 00:10:33,600
And your mother

201
00:10:34,080 --> 00:10:35,640
hanged herself the night your father

202
00:10:36,120 --> 00:10:37,120
was executed.

203
00:10:38,280 --> 00:10:38,960
You were the only one

204
00:10:38,960 --> 00:10:40,240
left in the family.

205
00:10:42,120 --> 00:10:43,280
I didn't realize your mother

206
00:10:43,280 --> 00:10:44,560
hid it from you so well.

207
00:10:44,920 --> 00:10:46,400
You really had no idea.

208
00:10:47,600 --> 00:10:49,080
But you have great literary flair.

209
00:10:49,320 --> 00:10:50,920
Completely different from your father.

210
00:10:51,760 --> 00:10:52,680
I felt sorry for you,

211
00:10:53,240 --> 00:10:54,400
so I brought you home

212
00:10:54,400 --> 00:10:55,760
and adopted you into the Fifth Branch.

213
00:10:59,040 --> 00:10:59,840
I see.

214
00:11:01,120 --> 00:11:02,560
You want me to marry Miss Yu

215
00:11:03,680 --> 00:11:04,960
because her father

216
00:11:06,040 --> 00:11:07,560
will help keep this secret.

217
00:11:08,320 --> 00:11:08,880
Yes.

218
00:11:10,320 --> 00:11:11,240
I expect

219
00:11:11,240 --> 00:11:12,520
you'll pass the metropolitan exam.

220
00:11:13,200 --> 00:11:14,200
But once you do,

221
00:11:14,200 --> 00:11:15,360
you'll draw attention.

222
00:11:15,840 --> 00:11:17,040
Especially from those

223
00:11:17,040 --> 00:11:18,720
who seek a marriage alliance with us.

224
00:11:19,520 --> 00:11:21,120
They'll dig into your background.

225
00:11:21,560 --> 00:11:22,440
And then

226
00:11:23,160 --> 00:11:24,160
this past

227
00:11:24,520 --> 00:11:25,720
will be hard to hide.

228
00:11:26,640 --> 00:11:28,240
Luckily, Kaiji thinks highly of you.

229
00:11:28,480 --> 00:11:29,720
And his daughter, Wanxue,

230
00:11:30,240 --> 00:11:31,560
has feelings for you.

231
00:11:32,880 --> 00:11:34,040
So we agreed

232
00:11:34,040 --> 00:11:34,960
to arrange the match

233
00:11:35,160 --> 00:11:36,160
before the metropolitan exam.

234
00:11:37,680 --> 00:11:38,360
Now you know

235
00:11:38,360 --> 00:11:39,680
everything.

236
00:11:39,960 --> 00:11:41,280
Marry Miss Yu

237
00:11:41,680 --> 00:11:42,320
and keep this secret

238
00:11:42,320 --> 00:11:43,400
as best you can?

239
00:11:43,920 --> 00:11:45,240
Or call off the match

240
00:11:45,840 --> 00:11:47,120
and face whatever comes

241
00:11:47,400 --> 00:11:48,640
after you pass the exam?

242
00:11:50,200 --> 00:11:51,320
You decide.

243
00:12:12,000 --> 00:12:12,600
Miss,

244
00:12:13,000 --> 00:12:14,960
a kite bears your feelings.

245
00:12:15,200 --> 00:12:16,760
Isn't giving it to Mr. Chen Xuanqing

246
00:12:17,120 --> 00:12:18,200
too forward?

247
00:12:19,560 --> 00:12:21,120
I want to be straightforward.

248
00:12:22,000 --> 00:12:23,920
Let him know how I feel.

249
00:12:24,160 --> 00:12:25,760
Then I'll know how he feels too.

250
00:12:26,360 --> 00:12:27,960
After all, I'm a girl.

251
00:12:28,240 --> 00:12:30,320
I can't keep meeting him in secret.

252
00:12:30,840 --> 00:12:33,040
And I don't want to spend my days

253
00:12:33,440 --> 00:12:34,880
guessing and second guessing.

254
00:12:35,840 --> 00:12:36,640
I'd rather just

255
00:12:36,720 --> 00:12:38,840
ask him once and be done with it.

256
00:12:42,280 --> 00:12:43,000
But

257
00:12:43,200 --> 00:12:44,800
I do think he

258
00:12:45,360 --> 00:12:46,880
has feelings for me.

259
00:12:47,600 --> 00:12:48,680
Why else

260
00:12:49,160 --> 00:12:50,520
would he ask me out?

261
00:13:01,560 --> 00:13:02,560
Are you sure she's going to

262
00:13:02,560 --> 00:13:03,560
see Chen Xuanqing?

263
00:13:04,200 --> 00:13:05,160
Most likely.

264
00:13:06,200 --> 00:13:07,160
Even if she isn't,

265
00:13:07,360 --> 00:13:08,240
why are you panicking?

266
00:13:08,600 --> 00:13:09,720
Just wait and see.

267
00:13:12,720 --> 00:13:13,960
It's flying!

268
00:13:14,120 --> 00:13:14,720
Miss!

269
00:13:16,240 --> 00:13:17,440
So high!

270
00:13:40,360 --> 00:13:41,920
It really is Chen Xuanqing.

271
00:13:42,480 --> 00:13:43,280
Let's follow them.

272
00:13:44,120 --> 00:13:44,760
Go over there.

273
00:13:44,920 --> 00:13:45,680
That place is small.

274
00:13:45,720 --> 00:13:46,520
Don't let them spot us.

275
00:13:48,360 --> 00:13:49,600
Okay, let's go.

276
00:13:50,840 --> 00:13:52,000
Miss Gu came early.

277
00:13:52,280 --> 00:13:53,360
She's flying a kite.

278
00:13:55,720 --> 00:13:56,440
A kite?

279
00:13:57,600 --> 00:13:58,280
Look.

280
00:14:22,040 --> 00:14:22,880
A kite.

281
00:14:23,280 --> 00:14:24,440
Miss Gu is...

282
00:14:26,280 --> 00:14:26,800
Xuanqing.

283
00:14:28,800 --> 00:14:29,320
Xuanqing?

284
00:14:34,720 --> 00:14:35,840
You go alone.

285
00:14:36,200 --> 00:14:37,000
I'm not going.

286
00:14:37,920 --> 00:14:38,760
When you get there,

287
00:14:39,120 --> 00:14:40,120
tell her

288
00:14:40,320 --> 00:14:41,080
something came up

289
00:14:41,280 --> 00:14:42,320
and I really can't make it.

290
00:14:45,600 --> 00:14:46,480
Give this

291
00:14:46,720 --> 00:14:47,520
to her for me.

292
00:14:49,120 --> 00:14:49,640
But...

293
00:14:50,720 --> 00:14:52,160
Why?

294
00:14:52,560 --> 00:14:54,240
Miss Gu has been waiting for you.

295
00:14:55,640 --> 00:14:56,360
Besides,

296
00:14:56,560 --> 00:14:58,120
we're the ones who asked her to come.

297
00:14:59,120 --> 00:14:59,800
I know.

298
00:15:00,480 --> 00:15:01,160
But

299
00:15:01,520 --> 00:15:02,440
I can't see her right now.

300
00:15:03,200 --> 00:15:04,000
It's not the right time.

301
00:15:04,880 --> 00:15:06,200
Are you sure about this?

302
00:15:20,840 --> 00:15:22,040
Thank you for the birthday gift.

303
00:15:23,240 --> 00:15:24,560
I hope one day

304
00:15:25,200 --> 00:15:26,520
I can be as brave

305
00:15:27,120 --> 00:15:27,840
and free

306
00:15:28,880 --> 00:15:29,560
as you.

307
00:15:40,640 --> 00:15:41,400
See?

308
00:15:42,360 --> 00:15:43,200
I wasn't lying.

309
00:15:43,720 --> 00:15:45,280
Told you Jinzhao and Chen Xuanqing

310
00:15:45,280 --> 00:15:46,440
were secretly seeing each other.

311
00:15:47,160 --> 00:15:48,360
Now you have something on her.

312
00:15:48,360 --> 00:15:49,560
She won't be able to bully you anymore.

313
00:15:50,600 --> 00:15:52,120
Jinzhao really is something.

314
00:15:52,280 --> 00:15:53,920
Her reputation is already this bad,

315
00:15:54,080 --> 00:15:55,240
and she still acts so carelessly.

316
00:15:55,840 --> 00:15:57,280
If this ever gets out...

317
00:15:57,280 --> 00:15:58,520
This must never get out!

318
00:15:59,920 --> 00:16:00,560
Swear

319
00:16:00,840 --> 00:16:01,400
you won't tell anyone

320
00:16:01,400 --> 00:16:02,480
what you saw today.

321
00:16:02,800 --> 00:16:03,600
You never saw

322
00:16:03,600 --> 00:16:04,480
Jinzhao

323
00:16:04,480 --> 00:16:05,240
or Chen Xuanqing.

324
00:16:05,560 --> 00:16:06,480
None of it ever happened.

325
00:16:06,760 --> 00:16:07,960
Have you lost your mind?

326
00:16:08,400 --> 00:16:09,760
What's wrong with you?

327
00:16:10,960 --> 00:16:11,760
You said it yourself,

328
00:16:11,880 --> 00:16:12,960
Jinzhao's reputation is already bad.

329
00:16:13,120 --> 00:16:13,960
If we add secret meetings

330
00:16:13,960 --> 00:16:14,840
to that,

331
00:16:15,000 --> 00:16:16,040
how could that end well?

332
00:16:16,720 --> 00:16:17,800
She's our older sister.

333
00:16:17,800 --> 00:16:19,040
If her reputation is ruined,

334
00:16:19,360 --> 00:16:21,120
it hurts both you and me.

335
00:16:21,480 --> 00:16:23,720
Since when are you so protective of her?

336
00:16:24,000 --> 00:16:24,640
She's family,

337
00:16:24,640 --> 00:16:25,880
not a stranger.

338
00:16:28,160 --> 00:16:29,960
Then tell Father and Mother.

339
00:16:30,240 --> 00:16:30,840
Not them either.

340
00:16:31,160 --> 00:16:31,960
If Father finds out,

341
00:16:31,960 --> 00:16:33,200
your mother will know too.

342
00:16:34,000 --> 00:16:35,520
I know what your mother

343
00:16:35,520 --> 00:16:36,400
and Nanny Zhou did

344
00:16:36,400 --> 00:16:37,320
to Jinzhao's marriage prospects.

345
00:16:37,800 --> 00:16:38,920
That was all a misunderstanding.

346
00:16:39,440 --> 00:16:40,760
Misunderstanding or not,

347
00:16:40,960 --> 00:16:42,040
I don't trust Father

348
00:16:42,320 --> 00:16:43,520
and I don't trust your mother.

349
00:16:44,240 --> 00:16:45,000
Don't worry.

350
00:16:45,480 --> 00:16:46,760
I know this has nothing to do with you.

351
00:16:47,080 --> 00:16:47,840
To me,

352
00:16:47,960 --> 00:16:49,400
you're you. They're them.

353
00:16:51,520 --> 00:16:52,280
Just promise me.

354
00:16:52,400 --> 00:16:53,480
Don't tell anyone

355
00:16:53,480 --> 00:16:54,160
what you saw today.

356
00:16:55,760 --> 00:16:56,560
Come on!

357
00:16:56,560 --> 00:16:57,200
Fine!

358
00:16:57,520 --> 00:16:58,120
You're so annoying.

359
00:16:58,840 --> 00:16:59,560
Don't you forget it!

360
00:17:02,520 --> 00:17:03,760
What time is it now?

361
00:17:04,359 --> 00:17:05,520
Why isn't he here yet?

362
00:17:06,560 --> 00:17:07,640
Miss, be patient.

363
00:17:07,960 --> 00:17:09,319
We arrived early.

364
00:17:13,480 --> 00:17:14,480
Miss, he's here.

365
00:17:18,160 --> 00:17:18,839
Miss Gu.

366
00:17:19,400 --> 00:17:20,200
Miss Qingpu.

367
00:17:21,000 --> 00:17:21,960
Where is your master?

368
00:17:22,359 --> 00:17:23,359
He had things to do

369
00:17:23,560 --> 00:17:24,520
at the academy today

370
00:17:24,720 --> 00:17:25,599
and couldn't get away,

371
00:17:26,160 --> 00:17:27,800
so he can't make it.

372
00:17:29,240 --> 00:17:30,080
I'm really sorry.

373
00:17:30,680 --> 00:17:31,680
He asked me

374
00:17:31,680 --> 00:17:32,920
to give you this.

375
00:17:44,320 --> 00:17:45,280
We had an agreement.

376
00:17:45,280 --> 00:17:46,560
Why did he suddenly not come?

377
00:17:46,880 --> 00:17:47,680
Qingpu,

378
00:17:47,880 --> 00:17:48,800
stop.

379
00:17:51,320 --> 00:17:52,760
I understand what your master

380
00:17:53,000 --> 00:17:53,720
means.

381
00:18:03,800 --> 00:18:04,680
Miss.

382
00:18:05,000 --> 00:18:06,320
He's just playing with you.

383
00:18:07,000 --> 00:18:07,600
What is Mr. Chen

384
00:18:07,600 --> 00:18:09,000
thinking anyway?

385
00:18:10,440 --> 00:18:11,760
Whatever he's thinking.

386
00:18:13,760 --> 00:18:15,000
I did my best.

387
00:18:15,680 --> 00:18:16,520
Him not showing up

388
00:18:16,760 --> 00:18:17,920
is on him.

389
00:18:19,040 --> 00:18:20,280
I just need to know I tried

390
00:18:20,800 --> 00:18:21,920
and I have no regrets.

391
00:19:01,680 --> 00:19:02,240
Miss.

392
00:19:02,800 --> 00:19:03,520
The Madam

393
00:19:03,520 --> 00:19:05,040
sent over some new jewelry

394
00:19:05,440 --> 00:19:07,080
for you to use during the New Year.

395
00:19:08,840 --> 00:19:09,920
That's thoughtful of her.

396
00:19:11,280 --> 00:19:11,960
Open it.

397
00:19:12,320 --> 00:19:13,040
Let me see.

398
00:19:24,120 --> 00:19:26,080
This color suits you.

399
00:19:26,360 --> 00:19:27,200
Put them on

400
00:19:27,440 --> 00:19:28,160
and let me see.

401
00:19:29,880 --> 00:19:30,600
Miss,

402
00:19:30,840 --> 00:19:31,680
I don't need them.

403
00:19:32,280 --> 00:19:33,120
Come on.

404
00:19:46,480 --> 00:19:47,760
This color is plain.

405
00:19:48,440 --> 00:19:49,440
Can't pair them

406
00:19:49,440 --> 00:19:50,760
with gold or gems.

407
00:19:52,480 --> 00:19:53,800
Just a

408
00:19:54,920 --> 00:19:56,480
simple bracelet then.

409
00:19:57,600 --> 00:19:58,400
This one works.

410
00:19:58,960 --> 00:19:59,880
Miss.

411
00:20:01,120 --> 00:20:01,840
Put it on.

412
00:20:14,800 --> 00:20:15,720
So pretty.

413
00:20:24,800 --> 00:20:25,720
Qingpu.

414
00:20:26,040 --> 00:20:26,720
I wish we could go back

415
00:20:26,720 --> 00:20:28,040
to Tongzhou for the New Year.

416
00:20:30,000 --> 00:20:30,960
I want to be

417
00:20:31,520 --> 00:20:32,960
with Grandmother,

418
00:20:34,840 --> 00:20:36,960
watching Iron Fireworks with my brother.

419
00:21:33,800 --> 00:21:34,840
When did you get here?

420
00:21:41,240 --> 00:21:42,360
I've been here for a while.

421
00:21:42,800 --> 00:21:44,080
Saw you were lost in thought,

422
00:21:44,360 --> 00:21:45,080
so I didn't want to disturb you.

423
00:21:45,400 --> 00:21:46,320
You

424
00:21:48,000 --> 00:21:49,680
are always so formal.

425
00:21:50,880 --> 00:21:51,880
I asked you here

426
00:21:51,880 --> 00:21:53,840
for your advice.

427
00:21:54,680 --> 00:21:56,840
Tongzhou's autumn tax this year

428
00:21:57,000 --> 00:22:00,160
is 50% higher than last year's.

429
00:22:01,160 --> 00:22:02,080
This is all thanks to

430
00:22:02,320 --> 00:22:03,960
the land equalization.

431
00:22:03,960 --> 00:22:04,960
I've been wondering

432
00:22:05,880 --> 00:22:07,800
how to spread the word

433
00:22:08,880 --> 00:22:10,240
about this success.

434
00:22:10,760 --> 00:22:12,080
Help me come up with something.

435
00:22:12,400 --> 00:22:14,120
Let the court

436
00:22:14,200 --> 00:22:15,760
and common people

437
00:22:15,760 --> 00:22:17,000
see the benefits

438
00:22:17,600 --> 00:22:18,720
of land surveying

439
00:22:19,280 --> 00:22:21,360
and the new tax laws.

440
00:22:21,840 --> 00:22:23,080
But we can't spend too much money.

441
00:22:23,520 --> 00:22:25,080
Can't just blow everything

442
00:22:25,240 --> 00:22:27,240
we've just earned.

443
00:22:32,120 --> 00:22:34,320
I actually do have an idea.

444
00:22:34,560 --> 00:22:35,080
Go on.

445
00:22:36,680 --> 00:22:37,440
In recent years,

446
00:22:38,080 --> 00:22:39,240
because the court has no money,

447
00:22:39,840 --> 00:22:40,640
we haven't seen

448
00:22:40,640 --> 00:22:42,240
the Aoshan Lantern display.

449
00:22:43,240 --> 00:22:43,880
So I think

450
00:22:44,480 --> 00:22:45,600
you should propose

451
00:22:45,760 --> 00:22:46,560
that the Ministry of Revenue

452
00:22:46,800 --> 00:22:47,400
fund them

453
00:22:47,920 --> 00:22:49,160
and set them up again this year.

454
00:22:49,360 --> 00:22:50,040
Then

455
00:22:50,240 --> 00:22:51,200
bring in

456
00:22:51,720 --> 00:22:53,640
the best folk performances

457
00:22:54,120 --> 00:22:54,520
from

458
00:22:54,800 --> 00:22:55,240
across the country,

459
00:22:55,560 --> 00:22:56,360
like street shows,

460
00:22:56,680 --> 00:22:57,280
dragon

461
00:22:57,840 --> 00:22:58,520
and lion dances,

462
00:22:58,600 --> 00:22:59,480
and Qinqiang opera.

463
00:22:59,880 --> 00:23:01,240
Especially the Iron Fireworks.

464
00:23:01,720 --> 00:23:03,000
They're lively and lucky.

465
00:23:03,400 --> 00:23:04,080
I

466
00:23:04,080 --> 00:23:05,240
haven't seen them in years.

467
00:23:05,680 --> 00:23:06,840
Let the people of the capital

468
00:23:06,840 --> 00:23:07,880
have a real celebration.

469
00:23:08,240 --> 00:23:09,720
And on top of that,

470
00:23:09,960 --> 00:23:10,880
set up more porridge kitchens

471
00:23:11,080 --> 00:23:12,040
to help the refugees.

472
00:23:12,400 --> 00:23:13,160
Let everyone

473
00:23:13,320 --> 00:23:14,320
have a proper New Year.

474
00:23:14,520 --> 00:23:15,000
Good.

475
00:23:15,200 --> 00:23:16,720
Great idea.

476
00:23:17,280 --> 00:23:19,000
Build up the momentum

477
00:23:19,200 --> 00:23:21,360
and make the people happy.

478
00:23:21,520 --> 00:23:21,960
Good.

479
00:23:22,160 --> 00:23:22,960
Excellent!

480
00:23:25,760 --> 00:23:26,440
But one thing.

481
00:23:26,920 --> 00:23:28,920
The grace should come from above.

482
00:23:29,160 --> 00:23:31,360
Instead of in Revenue's name,

483
00:23:31,360 --> 00:23:32,200
do it

484
00:23:35,480 --> 00:23:36,920
in His Majesty's name.

485
00:23:38,560 --> 00:23:39,240
Understood.

486
00:23:40,720 --> 00:23:41,720
That's wise of you.

487
00:23:49,840 --> 00:23:50,520
Take it easy.

488
00:23:52,720 --> 00:23:54,240
Why are you coughing again?

489
00:23:54,960 --> 00:23:55,880
I thought

490
00:23:56,360 --> 00:23:57,560
you were getting better.

491
00:23:58,240 --> 00:23:59,800
I wasn't coughing at all a few days ago.

492
00:24:00,360 --> 00:24:01,360
Don't know why

493
00:24:01,360 --> 00:24:03,000
it's back.

494
00:24:11,680 --> 00:24:12,320
Have some tea.

495
00:24:12,760 --> 00:24:13,360
Okay.

496
00:24:15,760 --> 00:24:17,120
This is the end of the year.

497
00:24:17,440 --> 00:24:18,520
Don't just stand there.

498
00:24:19,240 --> 00:24:20,000
Sit down.

499
00:24:24,400 --> 00:24:25,240
Sit.

500
00:24:48,000 --> 00:24:48,680
Rong.

501
00:24:50,040 --> 00:24:51,000
There's

502
00:24:51,360 --> 00:24:53,120
too much rich food in your bowl.

503
00:24:53,280 --> 00:24:54,480
It causes internal heartiness.

504
00:24:54,600 --> 00:24:55,840
Eat some vegetables.

505
00:24:56,520 --> 00:24:57,160
Thank you, Mother.

506
00:24:59,440 --> 00:25:00,040
Father.

507
00:25:07,720 --> 00:25:08,520
Thank you, Father.

508
00:25:11,640 --> 00:25:12,800
Have some vegetables.

509
00:25:14,440 --> 00:25:15,320
Thank you, Mother.

510
00:25:16,720 --> 00:25:17,840
Have some more.

511
00:25:23,240 --> 00:25:24,320
Grandmother.

512
00:25:24,520 --> 00:25:26,320
I want some meatballs.

513
00:25:27,760 --> 00:25:28,200
Here.

514
00:25:28,360 --> 00:25:30,280
Move the meatballs closer.

515
00:25:32,080 --> 00:25:33,400
Jinzhao

516
00:25:33,400 --> 00:25:35,320
loves meatballs.

517
00:25:35,600 --> 00:25:35,960
Here.

518
00:25:36,840 --> 00:25:38,560
Let me get you some.

519
00:25:41,080 --> 00:25:41,440
Here.

520
00:25:41,720 --> 00:25:42,360
Yao.

521
00:25:42,680 --> 00:25:44,320
Let me give you one too.

522
00:25:46,280 --> 00:25:47,200
Is it good?

523
00:25:47,680 --> 00:25:48,400
Yes.

524
00:26:07,960 --> 00:26:08,400
Here.

525
00:26:10,240 --> 00:26:11,360
Your grandmother says

526
00:26:11,360 --> 00:26:13,200
you love meatballs.

527
00:26:13,600 --> 00:26:14,360
Try it

528
00:26:14,560 --> 00:26:15,600
and see if it tastes the same

529
00:26:15,600 --> 00:26:16,080
as the one

530
00:26:16,080 --> 00:26:17,400
in Tongzhou.

531
00:26:29,960 --> 00:26:30,600
Delicious.

532
00:26:30,880 --> 00:26:31,640
Have some more.

533
00:26:31,920 --> 00:26:33,240
You've wasted away.

534
00:26:33,480 --> 00:26:35,280
Your clothes look so loose on you.

535
00:26:39,960 --> 00:26:41,200
I feel like

536
00:26:41,600 --> 00:26:42,600
you've been

537
00:26:43,160 --> 00:26:44,640
a bit down lately.

538
00:26:44,960 --> 00:26:46,640
Firecrackers!

539
00:26:48,520 --> 00:26:49,440
I want to go to the temple fair.

540
00:26:51,640 --> 00:26:53,160
I want to go too!

541
00:26:54,280 --> 00:26:54,920
Go on.

542
00:26:57,120 --> 00:26:57,520
Let's go.

543
00:26:57,560 --> 00:26:58,000
Let's go.

544
00:26:58,720 --> 00:26:59,640
Be careful.

545
00:26:59,800 --> 00:27:00,720
Got it!

546
00:27:01,880 --> 00:27:02,880
You should go too.

547
00:27:03,440 --> 00:27:04,640
Out with the old, in with the new.

548
00:27:05,000 --> 00:27:06,080
Don't carry

549
00:27:06,480 --> 00:27:07,520
the bad luck and unhappiness

550
00:27:07,640 --> 00:27:09,120
into the new year.

551
00:27:27,560 --> 00:27:28,200
Miss,

552
00:27:28,520 --> 00:27:29,560
time to drink your medicine.

553
00:27:33,160 --> 00:27:35,080
When will I be done with this medicine?

554
00:27:36,480 --> 00:27:37,880
I was perfectly fine.

555
00:27:38,600 --> 00:27:40,200
Why am I coughing again?

556
00:27:41,400 --> 00:27:43,120
Coughs come and go.

557
00:27:43,680 --> 00:27:44,480
It's been

558
00:27:44,760 --> 00:27:45,480
dry

559
00:27:45,640 --> 00:27:46,480
and dusty lately.

560
00:27:46,960 --> 00:27:48,560
That can easily trigger a cough.

561
00:27:49,680 --> 00:27:51,000
Just keep warm.

562
00:27:51,360 --> 00:27:52,000
Maybe

563
00:27:52,000 --> 00:27:53,520
you'll be better in a few days.

564
00:27:56,120 --> 00:27:57,760
I hope so.

565
00:28:07,760 --> 00:28:08,400
What's wrong?

566
00:28:17,680 --> 00:28:18,600
I'll go get a physician!

567
00:28:18,600 --> 00:28:19,240
Wait.

568
00:28:19,880 --> 00:28:21,200
It's the New Year.

569
00:28:22,080 --> 00:28:23,400
Where are you going to find a physician?

570
00:28:23,800 --> 00:28:24,760
But Miss...

571
00:28:24,880 --> 00:28:26,040
Don't say anything yet.

572
00:28:26,560 --> 00:28:27,320
Listen to me.

573
00:28:27,840 --> 00:28:28,600
But...

574
00:28:29,040 --> 00:28:29,760
This is

575
00:28:29,960 --> 00:28:31,040
Jinzhao's first New Year

576
00:28:31,040 --> 00:28:32,160
at home.

577
00:28:32,680 --> 00:28:34,000
If I tell them this,

578
00:28:34,960 --> 00:28:35,520
the kids

579
00:28:35,920 --> 00:28:37,160
won't have fun.

580
00:28:39,240 --> 00:28:40,120
Don't ruin the mood.

581
00:28:40,640 --> 00:28:42,680
Let's wait till after the New Year.

582
00:28:44,560 --> 00:28:45,320
The Madam's coughing so loud

583
00:28:45,320 --> 00:28:46,880
we can hear it across the courtyard.

584
00:28:47,400 --> 00:28:48,520
Did you call a physician?

585
00:28:48,880 --> 00:28:49,480
No.

586
00:28:50,080 --> 00:28:50,720
It seems the Madam

587
00:28:50,800 --> 00:28:52,520
had the Master keep the New Year's vigil.

588
00:28:52,520 --> 00:28:53,640
He's staying in the front courtyard.

589
00:28:53,760 --> 00:28:55,000
No need to go to the Madam's courtyard.

590
00:28:55,760 --> 00:28:57,480
Why did it suddenly get so bad?

591
00:28:58,000 --> 00:28:59,760
She was fine just a few days ago.

592
00:29:05,200 --> 00:29:06,440
Liuxiang, you can go now.

593
00:29:06,640 --> 00:29:07,960
I want to talk to Nanny Zhou alone.

594
00:29:16,120 --> 00:29:17,200
I added rhubarb

595
00:29:17,200 --> 00:29:18,040
to the Madam's medicine.

596
00:29:18,400 --> 00:29:19,200
What?

597
00:29:19,440 --> 00:29:20,880
Keep your voice down.

598
00:29:22,800 --> 00:29:24,280
How could you put that in her...

599
00:29:24,880 --> 00:29:25,440
Nanny Zhou.

600
00:29:25,440 --> 00:29:27,160
I really had no choice.

601
00:29:27,400 --> 00:29:28,680
Don't you see?

602
00:29:29,000 --> 00:29:30,240
Only if she's really sick

603
00:29:30,240 --> 00:29:31,560
will the Master let you run the household.

604
00:29:32,120 --> 00:29:33,920
Still, we can't do that.

605
00:29:34,600 --> 00:29:36,160
Think about Lan's coming-of-age ceremony

606
00:29:36,160 --> 00:29:37,280
and her future dowry.

607
00:29:38,400 --> 00:29:39,600
I did all of this.

608
00:29:40,000 --> 00:29:41,680
Just pretend I never told you.

609
00:29:41,920 --> 00:29:42,760
But we can't...

610
00:29:42,760 --> 00:29:43,680
The Master is here!

611
00:30:19,280 --> 00:30:20,440
Well, if it isn't Mr. Chen.

612
00:30:21,000 --> 00:30:22,440
Happy New Year.

613
00:30:22,680 --> 00:30:23,760
I wish you well.

614
00:30:24,960 --> 00:30:26,760
Mr. Su, happy New Year to you too.

615
00:30:28,400 --> 00:30:29,600
I rented

616
00:30:29,600 --> 00:30:30,880
a two-room suite up ahead.

617
00:30:31,160 --> 00:30:31,800
Would you care

618
00:30:31,920 --> 00:30:33,400
to come upstairs and take a look?

619
00:30:33,760 --> 00:30:34,840
Better than getting jostled around

620
00:30:34,840 --> 00:30:35,760
down here with the crowd.

621
00:30:37,880 --> 00:30:40,280
I'll go see the Aoshan Lantern display.

622
00:30:40,800 --> 00:30:41,400
I'll come to you

623
00:30:41,640 --> 00:30:42,680
in a bit.

624
00:30:43,400 --> 00:30:43,840
Alright.

625
00:30:43,960 --> 00:30:45,040
It's a deal.

626
00:31:18,640 --> 00:31:19,960
Rong, wait for me!

627
00:31:21,600 --> 00:31:22,720
I've seen plenty of dragon dances.

628
00:31:22,800 --> 00:31:24,240
But a fire-breathing dragon is rare.

629
00:31:24,400 --> 00:31:25,360
Watch out.

630
00:31:25,760 --> 00:31:26,320
I'm fine.

631
00:31:26,440 --> 00:31:27,240
Let's go somewhere else for a look.

632
00:31:28,240 --> 00:31:29,680
I was telling people

633
00:31:29,760 --> 00:31:30,640
that the New Year in the capital

634
00:31:30,640 --> 00:31:31,800
isn't as lively as in Tongzhou.

635
00:31:32,160 --> 00:31:32,880
Seems

636
00:31:33,000 --> 00:31:34,160
I was talking big.

637
00:31:34,600 --> 00:31:36,240
I think you were right.

638
00:31:36,360 --> 00:31:38,400
Sure, the capital is busier,

639
00:31:38,720 --> 00:31:40,160
but they don't have Iron Fireworks.

640
00:31:40,880 --> 00:31:41,800
So Tongzhou is still better.

641
00:31:45,880 --> 00:31:48,040
Walking over bridges cures all illnesses.

642
00:31:48,480 --> 00:31:49,440
Let's go do that.

643
00:31:51,800 --> 00:31:52,560
Rong.

644
00:31:56,480 --> 00:31:57,480
Where did he go?

645
00:31:58,080 --> 00:31:58,560
Let's go.

646
00:32:03,600 --> 00:32:05,240
Sir, it's just us now.

647
00:32:07,400 --> 00:32:07,960
Gentlemen,

648
00:32:08,160 --> 00:32:08,920
take care.

649
00:32:08,920 --> 00:32:09,360
Let's go.

650
00:32:09,960 --> 00:32:10,400
Okay.

651
00:32:10,400 --> 00:32:11,200
Come again tomorrow.

652
00:32:11,880 --> 00:32:12,360
Alright.

653
00:32:13,880 --> 00:32:14,280
Sir.

654
00:32:14,280 --> 00:32:15,040
Mr. Gu!

655
00:32:15,400 --> 00:32:16,920
You're not resting during the New Year?

656
00:32:17,560 --> 00:32:18,360
If no one else is resting,

657
00:32:18,360 --> 00:32:19,040
why should I?

658
00:32:19,520 --> 00:32:20,040
Alright, alright.

659
00:32:20,040 --> 00:32:20,880
Right this way.

660
00:32:21,680 --> 00:32:22,200
After you.

661
00:32:26,640 --> 00:32:27,640
Why are there so many people?

662
00:32:28,520 --> 00:32:29,560
This was your stupid idea.

663
00:32:30,240 --> 00:32:30,840
Sir,

664
00:32:31,200 --> 00:32:33,240
you asked me

665
00:32:33,240 --> 00:32:34,520
where the ladies of the capital

666
00:32:34,520 --> 00:32:35,920
go for New Year outings.

667
00:32:36,440 --> 00:32:37,640
I was just asking casually.

668
00:32:37,880 --> 00:32:38,680
You took it too seriously.

669
00:32:41,080 --> 00:32:41,720
Miss Gu?

670
00:32:42,240 --> 00:32:43,320
Mr. Ye.

671
00:32:53,600 --> 00:32:54,160
Sir,

672
00:32:54,560 --> 00:32:55,240
is Miss Gu

673
00:32:55,360 --> 00:32:56,520
still mad at you?

674
00:32:57,040 --> 00:32:57,720
No one

675
00:32:58,000 --> 00:32:58,880
is asking you to speak.

676
00:33:01,360 --> 00:33:01,920
Miss.

677
00:33:02,040 --> 00:33:03,240
He's the heir of Lord Changxing.

678
00:33:03,400 --> 00:33:04,440
Wouldn't it be rude

679
00:33:04,600 --> 00:33:05,880
if we just run off like this?

680
00:33:07,280 --> 00:33:08,480
If I stay,

681
00:33:08,840 --> 00:33:10,360
I'll only be even ruder!

682
00:33:10,880 --> 00:33:12,160
I'm doing this for his own good.

683
00:33:19,720 --> 00:33:20,280
Miss,

684
00:33:20,400 --> 00:33:21,040
didn't you say the capital

685
00:33:21,040 --> 00:33:22,200
doesn't have Iron Fireworks?

686
00:33:22,280 --> 00:33:23,880
Let's go up ahead and see!

687
00:33:24,000 --> 00:33:24,560
Okay.

688
00:33:26,200 --> 00:33:27,200
Sir, look over there.

689
00:33:56,840 --> 00:33:57,720
Let's go that way!

690
00:34:22,000 --> 00:34:23,120
So

691
00:34:24,239 --> 00:34:25,400
this is Iron Fireworks.

692
00:34:25,920 --> 00:34:26,960
You've never seen it before?

693
00:34:30,840 --> 00:34:31,600
I'm an idiot.

694
00:34:32,239 --> 00:34:33,000
I forgot you've been

695
00:34:33,199 --> 00:34:34,800
in central Sichuan all these years.

696
00:34:56,520 --> 00:34:57,560
I thought I wouldn't

697
00:34:57,720 --> 00:34:59,240
get to see Iron Fireworks this year.

698
00:35:00,160 --> 00:35:01,360
But here they are.

699
00:35:04,480 --> 00:35:06,440
So for every loss,

700
00:35:07,520 --> 00:35:08,560
there's a gain.

701
00:35:09,920 --> 00:35:10,920
Since that's the case,

702
00:35:11,240 --> 00:35:12,560
I shouldn't go looking for trouble.

703
00:35:16,640 --> 00:35:17,560
I can't believe the capital

704
00:35:17,560 --> 00:35:18,880
has Iron Fireworks.

705
00:35:20,440 --> 00:35:21,440
I wonder if Jinzhao

706
00:35:21,440 --> 00:35:22,200
saw it.

707
00:35:22,840 --> 00:35:24,240
She's always loved watching this.

708
00:35:25,040 --> 00:35:26,000
Grandmother even brought

709
00:35:26,320 --> 00:35:27,560
a Shanxi troupe

710
00:35:27,720 --> 00:35:28,760
to Tongzhou just for her.

711
00:35:29,360 --> 00:35:30,880
You should be thanking me.

712
00:35:32,480 --> 00:35:33,920
If I hadn't dragged you along,

713
00:35:34,440 --> 00:35:36,040
you'd have missed this grand spectacle.

714
00:35:48,320 --> 00:35:54,320
Long live the Great Yan!

715
00:35:55,000 --> 00:36:01,160
Long live the Great Yan!

716
00:36:01,680 --> 00:36:08,200
Long live the Great Yan!

717
00:36:08,800 --> 00:36:15,320
Long live the Great Yan!

718
00:36:16,080 --> 00:36:22,600
Long live the Great Yan!

719
00:36:23,080 --> 00:36:29,600
Long live the Great Yan!

720
00:36:29,960 --> 00:36:36,480
Long live the Great Yan!

721
00:36:37,000 --> 00:36:43,520
Long live the Great Yan!

722
00:36:44,000 --> 00:36:46,560
Long live the Great Yan!

723
00:36:46,920 --> 00:36:47,880
Mr. Chen Yanyun?

724
00:36:47,880 --> 00:36:50,160
Long live the Great Yan!

725
00:36:50,720 --> 00:36:53,600
Long live the Great Yan!

726
00:36:56,360 --> 00:36:57,240
Someone fell in the water!

727
00:36:57,240 --> 00:36:57,920
Help!

728
00:36:58,280 --> 00:36:59,080
Help!

729
00:36:59,080 --> 00:37:00,000
- Chen Yi.
- Sir.

730
00:37:01,440 --> 00:37:02,240
Hurry and save her!

731
00:37:02,480 --> 00:37:03,480
Someone fell in the water!

732
00:37:03,640 --> 00:37:04,200
Sir,

733
00:37:04,560 --> 00:37:05,680
I think someone fell in.

734
00:37:07,200 --> 00:37:08,120
Help!

735
00:37:08,160 --> 00:37:08,680
Let's go check it out.

736
00:37:08,760 --> 00:37:10,240
Someone fell in over there!

737
00:38:24,560 --> 00:38:25,760
He got her out.

738
00:38:26,880 --> 00:38:27,800
She's safe.

739
00:38:36,720 --> 00:38:37,320
Are you alright?

740
00:38:39,400 --> 00:38:40,440
It's you.

741
00:38:43,720 --> 00:38:44,480
Thank you, Mr. Chen.

742
00:38:44,480 --> 00:38:45,480
Miss! Miss!

743
00:38:48,400 --> 00:38:49,480
Are you alright?

744
00:38:50,280 --> 00:38:51,400
I'm fine.

745
00:38:57,480 --> 00:38:58,080
Sir,

746
00:38:58,560 --> 00:38:59,440
isn't that

747
00:38:59,440 --> 00:39:00,480
Mr. Chen Yanyun's guard?

748
00:39:01,000 --> 00:39:01,560
Could it be...

749
00:39:03,800 --> 00:39:04,480
It is him.

750
00:39:21,400 --> 00:39:22,160
Don't catch a cold.

751
00:39:24,800 --> 00:39:25,560
Thanks.

752
00:39:41,280 --> 00:39:41,920
Miss,

753
00:39:42,080 --> 00:39:43,440
Lord Guan saved you.

754
00:39:45,960 --> 00:39:47,080
No.

755
00:39:48,280 --> 00:39:49,520
It was Mr. Chen Yanyun.

756
00:39:59,840 --> 00:40:00,560
You mean the person

757
00:40:00,720 --> 00:40:01,720
who saved you at the back mountain

758
00:40:01,720 --> 00:40:02,280
in Tongzhou

759
00:40:02,280 --> 00:40:03,200
wasn't Mr. Chen Xuanqing,

760
00:40:03,320 --> 00:40:04,120
but Mr. Chen Yanyun?

761
00:40:06,040 --> 00:40:07,040
In the water,

762
00:40:07,280 --> 00:40:08,840
when he was pulling me to shore,

763
00:40:09,200 --> 00:40:10,760
it all came back to me.

764
00:40:13,320 --> 00:40:14,120
Miss,

765
00:40:14,200 --> 00:40:14,760
so

766
00:40:15,080 --> 00:40:15,960
Mr. Chen Yanyun

767
00:40:16,200 --> 00:40:17,640
has saved you three times now.

768
00:40:20,440 --> 00:40:21,520
Yeah.

769
00:40:25,160 --> 00:40:26,760
How am I ever going to

770
00:40:27,360 --> 00:40:28,920
repay such a favor?

771
00:41:15,080 --> 00:41:16,040
Why does my drawing

772
00:41:16,680 --> 00:41:18,240
look so much like...

773
00:41:35,600 --> 00:41:36,480
Jinzhao?

774
00:41:39,480 --> 00:41:39,920
Sir,

775
00:41:40,120 --> 00:41:41,120
the ginger soup is ready.

776
00:41:42,960 --> 00:41:43,800
Leave it over there.

777
00:41:44,200 --> 00:41:44,840
Yes.

778
00:41:55,040 --> 00:41:55,600
Chen Yi.

779
00:41:57,520 --> 00:41:58,160
Sir.

780
00:42:00,240 --> 00:42:01,200
Go

781
00:42:01,680 --> 00:42:02,760
invite Miss Gu over.

782
00:42:04,080 --> 00:42:04,720
Yes.

783
00:42:05,400 --> 00:42:06,000
Sir,

784
00:42:06,480 --> 00:42:07,800
what is this about?

785
00:42:08,240 --> 00:42:09,880
Just go invite her.

786
00:42:11,040 --> 00:42:11,600
Yes.

787
00:42:11,880 --> 00:42:12,640
I spoke out of turn.

788
00:42:17,000 --> 00:42:17,960
Wait. Come back.

789
00:42:23,360 --> 00:42:23,960
Never mind.

790
00:42:24,400 --> 00:42:25,200
You can go now.

791
00:42:28,920 --> 00:42:29,520
Yes.
